In this pa - per, we describe the program ReLie, written in the Computer Al- gebra System Reduce, which since 2008 is an open source program (http://www.reduce-algebra.com ) and is available for all platforms.
Its sourc e code is freely available at the url http://mat521.unime.it/oliveri .
It is written in a Lisp dialect (Portable Standard Lisp); sinceDecember 2008 it is an open source prog ram (available for all platforms at the url http://www.reduce-algebra.com ).
The source code of ReLie, as well as the user’s manual, can be found at the url http://mat521.unime.it/oliveri .
